kaalam காலம் time  
a period of time normally longer than a day  
s. time. duration  
பொழுது note. in hindu philosophy  
காலம் is said by the saivas to have proceeded from மோகினி maya  
and to be a coefficient cause with siva in the acts of creation  
preservation and destruction. it is time personified  
and according to the hindu metaphysicians  
one of the seven வித்தியாத் துவம். (சிவ. சி.)  
